main event: Multiple observers reported seeing bright lights in the sky near Stead AFB, Nevada, on 9 November 1963.
interesting points: The witnesses described the objects as bright lights that traveled at high speed,The sighting lasted approximately 10 minutes,Three observers confirmed the flight path and actions of the lights,The objects left trails of light as they moved,The initial conclusions suggested the sighting could be consistent with known aerial phenomena.
witness description: weather observer and air police personnel
